#import "../../../../../shared/environments.typ": *

==== Participants

    - n=60 ME/CFS patients (ages 18–60) with documented sleep disorders
    - Sleep disorder documentation via home sleep apnea testing: OSA (AHI $gt.eq$5 events/hour) or other sleep pathology (insomnia with documented sleep fragmentation, periodic breathing, etc.)
    - Mild to moderate severity (Bell scale 40–75)
    - No prior treatment with CPAP, BiPAP, or formal sleep disorder management
    - Willing to be randomized to immediate vs.\ delayed treatment

